---
title: Thanksgiving Anytime Chicken Sandos with Gravy, Cranberry Sauce & Potato-Carrot Jumble
description: Get ready to enjoy the flavors (and subsequent feelings) of Thanksgiving, all on a bun, at any time of year! First, you’ll pound chicken cutlets nice and thin, then brown them to crisp perfection. Meanwhile, you’re roasting a hearty carrot-onion-potato jumble in a hot oven (it’s “Thanksgiving anytime,” after all—something’s gotta roast!). Next, you’ll whisk up a buttery onion gravy, then spoon over pillowy brioche buns filled with chicken and shmeared with sweet-tart cranberry sauce. And boom—it’s Thanksgiving again (minus the annoying cousins!).
